Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了营救被蓝染虏走的织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入虚圈的一护等人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突进破面们的老巢虚夜宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶渡在与加廷拜恩战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:02:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体内的新能力得以觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在突然出现的十刃之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺伊多拉的面前无力招架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...切 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很弱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶渡被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是发过誓的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好要活着回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会对那些不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闯入这虚圈的家伙们的愚昧感到生气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 与阿洛尼洛对峙的露琪亚也陷入了危机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的能力叫做"喰虚"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬死亡之虚 将其能力和灵压为我所用的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙以志波海燕的身体返回虚圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我整个给吞噬掉才得到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个身体就是志波海燕的灵体本身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体内所有的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑中所有的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都完好地保留着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是将这些记忆和经历 读取出来再行动罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你见识见识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓十刃的刀剑解放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"喰虚"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在恐惧着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再感到恐惧一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是至今为止 我所吞噬掉的所有虚的力量显现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要以为十刃的刀剣解放 和一般的破面差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的"喰虚"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能将所有吞噬掉的虚的能力 全部同时表现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今为止所吞噬的虚的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是三万三千六百五十
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将是超过三万的虚之军团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一个人的对战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我...就只能到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为我杀害了海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才使得海燕大人的灵体落入虚的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为救自己而杀害了海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 让你难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你...我的心...才得以留存
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人的身体从敌人手里夺过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少这一点是对海燕大人的救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在心里告诉自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎这一点...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没有挥剑的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对海燕大人的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已没有挥剑的...力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见...了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊 海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然打我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我怎么叫你 摇你 你都不回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一落枕怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落枕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一边走路一边睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你丢下咯 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风吹到脸上的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林分出我前行的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:07:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草木的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪耀的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你到哪里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一棵棵的树木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不安 兴奋和温暖交织在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼之欲出的这份情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是西流魂街三区北端的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲤伏山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次带我修行的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是新入队员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是副队长志波海燕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这算什么招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边可是副队长在跟你报名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也应该自报家门 并请我多多指教才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字叫什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫朽木...露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK了 露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的怒声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的下级与上级的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十三番队欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们队上的队长身体不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上都是我在管理啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你也可以偶尔叫错 称我为海燕队长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这种平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却正是我所追求的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不够呢 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟儿飞过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这一瞬间我被鸟分散了注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二击就被海燕大人从左下方攻入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切我都记得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是非常专注的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是想吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个超级自我中心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不是的啦 海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦 别在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海...海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱扔出了鞘的刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都会肚子饿的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用不着这么害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时的我 心中有所不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入队仪式顺利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几席啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我的能力还无法...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一入队马上就成为席官...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就缺乏剑术的天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知罪梦之壁 仅立其上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破道之三十三 苍火坠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在灵术院时鬼道的成绩还算不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在护廷队中也只属一般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的可以呆在护廷十三队中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟为了什么而呆在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟为了什么而在这里的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情不是明摆着的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了守护而战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要守护什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么...你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啦 那个啦 很多东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来实在是很模糊不清的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其它更明确一些的回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明确的回答啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木 你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有听过我们队长的一贯主张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗分为两种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护生命的战斗和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守卫尊严的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是浮竹队长的一贯主张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:14:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得无论哪种战斗 最终都是在守护相同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相同的东西...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃... 好酸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我可是很认真地在说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我问你啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得"心"在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...这个嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就是在这... 附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得 心啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你接触的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心就在我们之间生成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心不在身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思索什么的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想念谁的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心就在那里生成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果世界上只有自己孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不存在什么心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人确实是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么好烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你衷心希望能呆在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你的心就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心在这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这就是你呆在这里的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将来你战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事绝对不能做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的身体就是魂魄本身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死后身体自然会化作尘土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为包围尸魂界的灵子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时心会去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心要交给同伴保管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给同伴...保管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将心交给同伴保管的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心就会在那个人体内继续生存
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对不能独自死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心要交给同伴保管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有意识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命真大 不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是可怜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你怎样苟延残喘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法改变你不能斩杀我的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还留有握刀柄的力气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你想起了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用折断的刀战斗的蠢事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太碍眼了 放下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:18:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心的所在之处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你身体里确实是海燕大人的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 海燕大人并不在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经交给我保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十刃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦 好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 蓝染大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝染大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说过的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我跟着你 就会从一切痛苦中解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦 好痛苦 好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 我不要 我不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对...不会...认同的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别死啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解什么是孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为被捕者的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解什么是喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴前来搭救时的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那些同伴受伤被打倒时的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在... 就去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺伊多拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天您用手指 指着地面是在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是用这种方法 寻找整个虚夜宫中的灵压
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情也可以做得到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也试试
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 泰斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.47,0:23:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们别无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神图鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有钱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次的预算已经用得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都太乱花钱了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.40,0:24:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长您用得最多了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.54,0:24:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 为了快速凑集经费
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.96,0:24:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拍些名人的生活照来卖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.53,0:24:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在现世搞偷拍的狗仔师都赚了大钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是护廷十三队的明星们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解散
